channel.title: Some flower
channel.description:
We don't have anything saying photography here so I'll just post in here. Normally I post at a dedicated photography forum, but I haven't posted in a while here and I feel very proud of myself.
Almost all of my time that went to modeling before is now in school, and photography because I just bought a new lens with birthday money.
I think I outdid myself on this one. Let me know what you think. I think it's one of the best pictures I've ever taken.
